profile: Siding, Stucco, Stone, Brick, Masonry and Fireplaces From design to installation, Stone Selex Design is a premier company with over 20 years of experience providing both residential and commercial customers with quality installation and a high level of customer satisfaction. Stone Selex Design is committed to providing full service installation for your exterior or interior stone veneer project. We also provide installation of stone veneer, stucco, brick, masonry and fireplace transformations. Design your own project with the NEW Stone Veneer Visualizer and have Stone Selex Design install it for you. The Visualizer gives you the ability to envision your project from the comfort of your computer screen. It has the power to transform a photo of your home into a professional digital rendering by adding siding, stucco and stone. Make your home the talk of the neighbourhood with stone and stucco, or stone and brick, or siding and brick, stone tile and wood siding. The possibilities of style and colour combinations are endless. A Stone Selex Design project manager will help you with each stage of your project from where to add stone, stucco, siding, brick and masonry and provide you with a quote for our installation services provided by our experienced masonry installers. If itâ€™s a fireplace that you want to create or just simply add stone or masonry, Stone Selex Design and the visualizer can help you with this too. While you are in the planning stages of your fireplaces transformation the visualizer is a great tool to use. Look through photos for ideas and see what others are doing and then come to Stone Selex Design and ask us to install it for you. Visit us here: https://twitter.com/StoneSelex https://www.facebook.com/StoneSelexInc/

Fireplacewest.ca is a premier gas fireplace contractor.

We supply and install Napoleon, Regency, Vermont Castings and lately, a lot of Valor gas inserts.  These are the best of Canadian and North American brands.

We are unique.  Our mission is to have none to zero warranty work and to provide a complete package from the gas fireplace sale to finished drywall and stone.  All of our pics are our work alone. A bit of Catholic guilt ensures a timely response to feedback.  We are good listeners.

Company trends have to do complete swaps, wood to gas conversions with full finishing.
 
Let's talk fireplaces.  Robin@fireplacewest.  613-720-3186.

profile:
Impressive Climate Control has brought the best in comfort control to the Ottawa area for over a decade and excels at providing our valued customers with highly efficient, reliable and affordable heating, air conditioning, and indoor air quality products. We insist that the products we install in our customer's homes and businesses offer the same performance and value we expect ourselves. For this reason we proudly carry top of the line brand names and HVAC systems such as furnaces, gas or wood fireplaces and stoves, air conditioners, mini split air conditioners, heat pumps, boilers, tankless water heaters, hot water tanks, ventilators, air handlers, air cleaners and humidifiers all nicely set up in our showroom. Impressive provides service and maintenance on all HVAC products as well as affordable protection plans to protect your home comfort investements. Best of all, Impressive offers attractive HVAC rental plans in both heating and cooling home comfort systems for home owners in the Ottawa valley area.

***

Impressive Climate Control is rated A+ for its outstanding customer service as an accredited member of Better Business Bureau and it is an active member of the Heating, Refrigeration and Air Conditioning Institute of Canada (HRAI).Our professionally trained technicians are TSSA licensed and qualified to service all makes and models of heating and cooling systems in residential homes or light commercial units.
